title: Dishwasher TUB TRIMS KIT
description: Dishwasher TUB TRIMS KIT ★★★★★ ★★★★★ 3 Reviews PartSelect Number PS16742698 Manufacturer Part Number WD01X31858 This part is the replacement tub trim for your dishwasher. It is approximately 26 inches long and 2 inches wide. The tub trim is found on the exterior of the dishwasher, and the main reason you would want to replace it is if it is cracked, worn, or damaged. This tub trim is sold individually and is an OEM part sourced directly from the manufacturer.

installationInstructions.author: jeff from FORT COLLINS, CO
installationInstructions.title: leaking from somewhere around tub
installationInstructions.content: the actual gasket tub seal was easy, 10 minutes. The trim tub gaskets were a pain because I had to uninstall the dishwasher (not plumbing or electrical) then pull it out from the cabinet, remove old trim and re-install. Re-leveled dishwasher, screwed into side of cabinets but it still leaks. Can't figure out where but after replacing all the trim and gaskets its very frustrating.
